pullrequest.title: Server generates unique model names in case of overlap -> default

content.raw: I'm sorry I missed that. I believe it's due to one of the problems this PR fixed, which is the `gz model` tool being able to spawn two different models with the same name. We could move the test for deleting a model to be in between the two spawn tests for example.
content.html: I'm sorry I missed that. I believe it's due to one of the problems this PR fixed, which is the gz model tool being able to spawn two different models with the same name. We could move the test for deleting a model to be in between the two spawn tests for example.
